metadata.name: Pink's
metadata.description:
Photography at night has a certain thrill. A popular joint at the heart of Los Angeles, Pink's Hot Dogs carries generations of memories since 1939. It's neon lights provides the ideal setting for an image full of contrast and vibrance and the human presence tells a story about the daily affair and interactions at the place.
